reviewText: Worst movies I have seen from that period. Both movies are primarily orgy scenes pieced together from pieces off the cutting room floor. They are also very short for "features". Very boring, like practice scenes.
Perfect in everything, no complaint, and it arrived on time too.
Simply not my cup of tea:  several young men and women having explicit sex in a large parlor-sort of room.  No real plot.
One of the best in this series
